 Outkast 起诉 EDM 组合 ATLiens 因商标存在明显“品牌保护问题” https://www.nme.com/news/music/outkast-sue-edm-duo-atliens-in-apparent-brand-protection-issue-over-trademark-3786402?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=outkast-sue- edm-duo-atliens 明显品牌保护问题商标问题Daniel PetersSat, 24 Aug 2024 08:04:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsEDMRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3786402 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="流浪者ATLiens" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>嘻哈偶像的代表声称“不幸的是，友好解决此事的努力没有成功”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/outkast-sue-edm-duo-atliens-in-apparent-brand-protection-issue-over-trademark-3786402">Outkast 起诉 EDM 组合 ATLiens 的商标“品牌保护问题”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="流浪者ATLiens" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OutKast-2014-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/outkast">Outkast</a>正在起诉名为 ATLiens 的 EDM 二人组，理由是涉及其名称的明显“品牌保护问题”，代表其商标控股公司的律师表示。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-romy-and-sampha-team-up-to-cover-andre-3000s-me-my-to-bury-your-parents-3598029">聆听 Romy 和 Sampha 合作翻唱 André 3000 的《Me &amp; My (To Bury Your Parent)》</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://allhiphop.com/news/exclusive-outkast-sues-edm-duo-over-atliens-trademark/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>AllNewHipHop</em></a>报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">André 3000</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-boi">Big Boi</a>的商标控股公司 High Schoolers LLC 已对 ATLiens Touring, Inc. 提起诉讼，声称这对嘻哈二人组首先创造了“ATLiens”一词，并已于 1996 年将其注册为商标。</p><p>根据<em>AllNewHipHop</em>的法庭文件，EDM 二人组于 2020 年向美国专利局注册了 ATLiens 名称作为服务商标，声称他们自 2012 年以来一直在使用该名称。拥有 EDM 二人组商标的公司是 ATLiens Touring, Inc .，而 Outkast 的公司（诉讼中的官方原告）是 High Schoolers, LLC。</p><p>文件中写道：“被告已经并将继续在该州和地区出售音乐会门票并进行现场表演，其下一场演出将于 2025 年 2 月 15 日在佐治亚州亚特兰大的可口可乐 Roxy 剧院举行。”</p><p> “被告还通过其互动网站向本州和本地区的消费者做广告、提供销售和销售产品，包括带有 ATLIENS 标志的商品。”</p><p>律师 Abigail J. Remore 和 Peter E. Nussbaum 代表 High Schoolers LLC 和 André 3000 告诉<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/outkast-sue-edm-duo-atliens-for-trademark-infringement/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a> ：“这是一个基本的品牌保护问题。遗憾的是，友好解决此事的努力并未成功，Outkast 因此不得不提起诉讼，以保护其创建并持续使用了近 30 年的宝贵名称和商标 ATLIENS。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_BUdjVPEsB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; fle